wiki.summary: "Hentai" (stylized in all caps) is the fourth single from Rosalía's third studio album, Motomami. The song is a "delicate" piano ballad with pulsing electronic beats that explores the pleasures of sexual intercourse and female sexuality. The song was previously teased on TikTok and highly criticized because of its lyrics due to it being named about a subgenre of the Japanese genres of manga and anime, characterized by overtly sexualized characters. It was released on March 16, 2022. Read more on Last.fm.
